summary: MY 2001 FORD TAURUS SHAKES AT HIGHWAY SPEEDS.  PROBLEM HAS BEEN BLAMED ON EVERYTHING.  TIRES HAVE BEEN REPLACED AND BALANCED, ROTORS HAVE BEEN REPLACED (FOR THE 2ND TIME IN THIS CARS YOUNG LIFE), AND THE BRAKE PADS HAVE BEEN REPLACED.   I JUST WANT MY CAR TO STOP SHAKING.  SEEMS LIKE WE'RE PLAYING EENY,MEENY,MINY, MOE WITH MY MONEY AND TIME.  STILL NO RESOLUTION. *JB
